msgctxt "an9.46:0.1"
msgid "Aṅguttara Nikāya 9 "
msgstr "Numbered Discourses 9 "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "an9.46:0.2"
msgid "5. Sāmaññavagga "
msgstr "5. Similarity "

#. HTML: </p><h1>
msgctxt "an9.46:0.3"
msgid "46. Sandiṭṭhikadhammasutta "
msgstr "46. In This Very Life "

#. HTML: </h1></div><p>
#. REF: sc1
msgctxt "an9.46:1.1"
msgid "“‘Sandiṭṭhiko dhammo, sandiṭṭhiko dhammo’ti, āvuso, vuccati. "
msgstr "“Reverend, they speak of ‘a teaching visible in this very life’. "

msgctxt "an9.46:1.2"
msgid "Kittāvatā nu kho, āvuso, sandiṭṭhiko dhammo vutto bhagavatā”ti? "
msgstr "In what way did the Buddha speak of a teaching visible in this very life?” "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: sc2
msgctxt "an9.46:2.1"
msgid "“Idhāvuso, bhikkhu vivicceva kāmehi … pe … paṭhamaṃ jhānaṃ upasampajja viharati. "
msgstr "“First, take a mendicant who, quite secluded from sensual pleasures … enters and remains in the first absorption. "

msgctxt "an9.46:2.2"
msgid "Ettāvatāpi kho, āvuso, sandiṭṭhiko dhammo vutto bhagavatā pariyāyena … pe …. "
msgstr "To this extent the Buddha spoke of the teaching visible in this very life in a qualified sense. … "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: sc3
msgctxt "an9.46:3.1"
msgid "Puna caparaṃ, āvuso, bhikkhu sabbaso nevasaññānāsaññāyatanaṃ samatikkamma saññāvedayitanirodhaṃ upasampajja viharati, paññāya cassa disvā āsavā parikkhīṇā honti. "
msgstr "Furthermore, take a mendicant who, going totally beyond the dimension of neither perception nor non-perception, enters and remains in the cessation of perception and feeling. And, having seen with wisdom, their defilements come to an end. "

msgctxt "an9.46:3.2"
msgid "Ettāvatāpi kho, āvuso, sandiṭṭhiko dhammo vutto bhagavatā nippariyāyenā”ti. "
msgstr "To this extent the Buddha spoke of the teaching visible in this very life in a definitive sense.” "

#. HTML: </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "an9.46:3.3"
msgid "Pañcamaṃ. "
msgstr ""

#. HTML: </p></article></section></body></html>
